You just couldn't let me go, could you?

1757
02:13:29,386 --> 02:13:33,300
就是这样  当不可阻挡的力量
This is what happens when an unstoppable force...

1758
02:13:33,473 --> 02:13:37,934
遇到屹然不动的阻挡
...meets an immovable object.

1759
02:13:38,520 --> 02:13:43,941
