02:19:16,858 --> 02:19:18,518
轮到我了
My turn.

1844
02:19:25,450 --> 02:19:27,443
哈维  你是对的
Harvey, you're right.

1845
02:19:28,495 --> 02:19:31,116
瑞秋的死是我的错
Rachel's death was my fault.

1846
02:19:34,209 --> 02:19:36,664
求你别错罚到孩子身上
Please don't punish the boy.

1847
02:19:37,754 --> 02:19:40,957
-求你  罚我就行  -我正要
- please, punish me. - I'm about to.

1848
02:19:42,926 --> 02:19:44,883
告诉你儿子  他会没事的  戈登
Tell your boy he's gonna be all right, gordon.

1849
02:19:45,345 --> 02:19:46,969
向他说谎
Lie...

1850
02:19:47,472 --> 02:19:48,587
就像我对瑞秋说谎
...like I lied.

1851
02:19:52,352 --> 02:19:53,930
没事的  孩子
It's going to be all right, son.

1852
02:20:32,350 --> 02:20:35,185
爸爸  爸爸  他没事吧
Dad? daddy, is he okay?

1853
02:20:51,703 --> 02:20:53,861
-谢谢  -你没必要谢我
- thank you. - you don't have to thank me.

1854
02:20:54,497 --> 02:20:56,289
我当然得谢你
Yes, I do.

1855
02:21:00,545 --> 02:21:01,874
小丑赢了
The Joker won.

1856
02:21:04,299 --> 02:21:07,169
哈维的苦心经营，他为之奋斗的一切…
Harvey's prosecution, everything he fought for...

1857
02:21:07,719 --> 02:21:09,462
都付之东流
...undone.

1858
02:21:09,971 --> 02:21:12,331
你给我们的重振城市的机会
Whatever chance you gave us at fixing

1859
02:21:12,332 --> 02:21:14,882
也随着哈维的身败名裂而消失了
Our city dies with Harvey's reputation

1860
02:21:15,060 --> 02:21:16,222
我们把一切寄托在他身上
We bet it all on him.

1861
02:21:17,562 --> 02:21:20,433
小丑却把他拉下宝座，让他坠入深渊
The Joker took the best of us and tore him down.

1862
02:21:21,024 --> 02:21:22,435
人们会失去希望
People will lose hope.

1863
02:21:22,609 --> 02:21:24,352
他们不会的
They won't.

1864
02:21:26,863 --> 02:21:28,737
他们永远不会知道他做了什么
They must never know what he did.

1865
02:21:28,907 --> 02:21:30,734
五个人死了
Five dead.

1866
02:21:31,034 --> 02:21:32,314
两个是警察
Two of them cops.

1867
02:21:32,494 --> 02:21:34,949
- 你没法抹煞这件事…  - 不
- you can't sweep that... - no.

1868
02:21:39,751 --> 02:21:42,586
不能让小丑得逞
But the Joker cannot win.

1869
02:21:47,842 --> 02:21:51,046
高谭需要它真正的英雄
Gotham needs its true hero.

1870
02:21:57,435 --> 02:22:00,472
- 不  - 要么舍生取义 作为英雄而死…
- no. - you either die a hero...

1871
02:22:00,647 --> 02:22:05,108
要么苟活  坐等与恶人同流合污
...or you live long enough to see yourself become the villain.

1872
02:22:05,276 --> 02:22:07,103
我可以这样做
I can do those things...

1873
02:22:07,529 --> 02:22:10,565
因为我不是个英雄  不像登特
...because I'm not a hero, not like Dent.

1874
02:22:13,576 --> 02:22:16,447
是我杀了那些人  我可以如此
I killed those people. that's what I can be.

1875
02:22:16,621 --> 02:22:18,530
不行 绝对不行 你不是
No, no, you can't. you're not.

1876
02:22:18,707 --> 02:22:21,280
高谭需要什么人  我就是什么
I'm whatever gotham needs me to be.

1877
02:22:22,961 --> 02:22:24,076
叫他们进来吧
Call it in.

1878
02:22:27,382 --> 02:22:29,125
一个英雄
A hero.

1879
02:22:29,301 --> 02:22:32,551
或许我们不配拥有  但我们确实需要
Not the hero we deserved, but the hero we needed.

1880
02:22:33,138 --> 02:22:35,676
就像一个骑士
Nothing less than a knight...

1881
02:22:36,224 --> 02:22:37,932
闪耀着光明
...shining.

1882
02:22:38,560 --> 02:22:40,184
他们会追捕你
They'll hunt you.

1883
02:22:40,353 --> 02:22:42,145
你也要追捕我
You'll hunt me.

1884
02:22:42,647 --> 02:22:44,604
还要声讨我
You'll condemn me.

1885
02:22:45,317 --> 02:22:47,605
在我身后放狗追逐
Set the dogs on me.

1886
02:22:51,364 --> 02:22:53,653
因为事情必须如此
Because that's what needs to happen.

1887
02:22:54,826 --> 02:22:56,735
因为有时
Because sometimes...

1888
02:22:56,911 --> 02:22:59,070
真相并不一定美好
... the truth isn't good enough.

1889
02:22:59,956 --> 02:23:02,245
有时人们应该得到更多
Sometimes people deserve more.

1890
02:23:05,712 --> 02:23:09,626
有些时候 人们的信念必须得到回报
Sometimes people deserve to have their faith rewarded.

1891
02:23:28,026 --> 02:23:29,686
蝙蝠侠
Batman.

1892
02:23:31,613 --> 02:23:33,356
蝙蝠侠
Batman!

1893
02:23:34,157 --> 02:23:36,114
爸爸  他为什么要跑？
Why's he running, dad?

1894
02:23:37,160 --> 02:23:38,488
因为我们得抓他
Because we have to chase him.

1895
02:23:38,662 --> 02:23:41,532
好 大家进去！快！
Okay, we're going in! go, go! move!

1896
02:23:47,629 --> 02:23:49,206
可他并没做错什么
He didn't do anything wrong.

1897
02:23:51,967 --> 02:23:57,553
因为高谭需要他这样的英雄  但还不是现在
Because he's the hero gotham deserves, but not the one it needs right now.

1898
02:23:58,974 --> 02:24:00,005
所以我们要追捕他
So we'll hunt him...

1899
02:24:03,144 --> 02:24:05,220
因为他能承受这一切
... because he can take it.

1900
02:24:07,732 --> 02:24:10,223
因为他不是我们心目中的英雄
Because he's not our hero.

1901
02:24:17,784 --> 02:24:18,982
他是静默的守望者
He's a silent guardian...

1902
02:24:20,161 --> 02:24:22,035
时刻警惕的卫士
...a watchful protector.

1903
02:24:24,541 --> 02:24:25,821
暗夜中的骑士
A dark knight.

